author: BBC News
description:
Qatar has said no Gulf state is safe after Israeli strikes in Doha this week.
 
Dr Majed Al-Ansari, a spokesman for the Qatari Ministry of Foreign Affairs, spoke to BBC News in Doha after the strikes on a residential compound in the Qatari capital.
 
The attacks, which targeted senior members of Hamas, have been condemned by the United Nations.
 
Israeli Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu said it was justified because it targeted the "terrorist masterminds" behind the 7 October 2023 Hamas attack on Israel.

author: BBC News
description:
Charlie Kirk was one of America's loudest political voices, with a huge audience amongst young voters.
 
The 31-year-old was an ally of Donald Trump, and a right-wing activist. 
 
Kirk was shot dead on Wednesday during an open-air speaking event in Orem, Utah. His suspected killer, Tyler Robinson, was arrested on Thursday night after surrendering to police.
